New Pings/Notification Roles

We’re updating our notification system to make game pings more relevant and targeted.

The @Game Pings role is being removed and replaced with the following:
@Star Atlas UE5 Pings 
@SAGE Pings 
@Holosim Pings 

To manage your ping preferences, head to ⁠🔔┃choose-pings  or click “Channels & Roles” at the top left of the server. Thanks everyone!
